Spruce Woods Provincial Park will host the provincial high school cross-country running championships today. 
The junior varsity boys will be first off the starting line at noon, followed by the varsity boys at 12:30, the JV girls at 1 and the varsity girls at 1:30 p.m. Please subscribe to view full article.
